---
By: John Chrysostom
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 54
    Verse: 22
Tags:
  - Charity
---
Charity is, indeed, a great thing, and a gift offered, and when it is
rightly ordered, likens us to God himself, as far as that is possible;
for it is charity that makes the man.
